  (text "IO: slot connector split into power blades (>=30A, first-mate/last-break) +\nsignal row (CAN, HW_EN, slot straps, PRESENT->PGND). Physical connector family\nchosen at the batch PCB pass with the backplane (docs/08 s.12) - generic\nheaders stand in so the netlist is final. Fan: 5V, low-side PWM switch."
    (at 218.44 173.99 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)))
